sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager

participant UI as Dependency Reporting UI
participant BFF as Dependency Management BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant DEP as Dependency Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

PM->>UI: Open dependency reporting / audit view
UI->>BFF: Load dependency reporting
BFF->>ORCH: Get reporting view
ORCH->>DEP: Fetch dependency reporting dataset
DEP->>READDB: Read project_dependency, project_dependency_status_history,<br/> project_dependency_document
READDB-->>DEP: Reporting data
DEP-->>ORCH: Reporting response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show dependency trail and <br/>closure-ready artefacts
